  "title": "M&E BIM Modeller cum Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:<br>\n• Produce M&amp;E BIM model deliverables for design, documentation and fabrication purpose.<br>\n• Ensure that M&amp;E BIM models are delivered with professionalism (Quality, due diligence and timeliness)<br>\n• Prepare models for Clash Detection Coordination<br>\n• Identify issues for BIM Managers where discrepancies occur during design production.<br>\n• Ensure BIM models are modelled with the correct BIM parameters and attributes for BIM assisted Quantification, 4 D simulation<br>\n• The BIM modeller’s overall responsibility is to create BIM content and extracting production documents for the purpose of delivering a BIM assisted project.<br>\n• Produce accurate AUTOCAD and REVIT BIM drawing according to project requirements;<br>\n• To complete documentation from detailed engineering drawings, construction drawings, shop drawings, and as-built drawings, and produce drawing sets<br>\n• They assist BIM Coordinators in creating BIM models for projects. Assist in building basic BIM libraries.<br>\n• Preparation of M&amp;E shop drawings, and As-built drawing;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements:<br>\n• Diploma/Degree in Electrical/Mechanical Engineering;<br>\n• Certificate from BCA BIM modelling course or equivalent<br>\n• Minimum 3 years of work experience in M&amp;E field, preferably in building construction industry;<br>\n• Proficient in AUTOCAD and MEP Revit software<br>\n• Able to work independently under stress and pressure;<br>\n• Good work attitude with passion and drive</p>",
